RelatedSentence: HAMPTONBURGH >> Orange County resident Orysia Dmytrenko is heading to Ukraine , the country where her parents were born , to be one of the international election observers for the presidential and local elections this coming weekend .
This will be her second time serving as an international election observer , having performed the same role 10 years ago .

She said feels a special bond to the country and its people but also feels lucky that her parents moved to the United States , where she was born .

Dmytrenko will be deployed as part of a team to the eastern part of Ukraine , where there has been recent unrest by separatists , backed by Russia , who are attempting to destabilize the interim government in Kiev .
